posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 187260851', 'Rent: $1,495 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 08/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats & Small Dogs Only', 'This modern one bedroom, one bathroom in Wicker Park features an updated kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, hardwood floors throughout, exposed brick wall, high ceilings, central air and heat.', 'This location is pet friendly, and has an on-site laundry facility.', 'The building is located close to the Division Blue Line, Clybourn Metra, New City shopping center is a short bus ride away and there are many restaurants and bars within walking distance.', 'The building is close to I-90 and Pulaski Park is across the street!', 'FEATURES', 'Cats OK', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Central Air', 'Dishwasher', 'Dogs under 25lbs', 'Exposed Brick', 'Granite Counter Tops', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Laundry', 'Laundry in Building', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Walk-In Closet', 'Daniel Ennion', 'Broker 881730', 'Square One Realty', '<URL>']
